---
description: Room schema — real migrations only
globs: app/**/Migrations.kt,app/**/NurseryDatabase.kt,app/**/entity/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Room migrations

- No `fallbackToDestructiveMigration` — the local DB must never be silently wiped in production.
- Every schema change needs a real `Migration` in `Migrations.kt`; bump version in `NurseryDatabase.kt`.
- Plant list is replaced wholesale on sync; receipt/cull data is not.
